---
title: American-Spiced Chicken Tenders with Smokey Mash & Greens
description: You don’t have to own a charcoal grill to get that wonderful smoked flavour on your plate!  Just add our smokey aioli to mashed potato instead of butter, and smother chicken tenders with our All-American spice blend. Tastes just like Houston!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d6f40e331442e000f37dbe7-a7b4f887.jpg
